gdalena-bay-imaginal-disk-review-3784463">“ Imaginal Disk</a> ”的创作非常鼓舞人心。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Magdalena湾的封面封面戴维·鲍伊（David Bowie" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rD0hunq8zL8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>解释他们为什么决定在大多数情况下坚持原始歌曲时，云母分享了：“当您非常喜欢一首歌并且您知道自己喜欢什么时，您也想让它自己做一点，就像您真正弄乱了它吗？”</p><p> “我只是想让它感觉像我一样，”她说改变人声以适合自己的范围和风格。 “因为显然我喜欢鲍伊的嗓音，但不幸的是，我听起来像他一样。</p><p>二人组将接下来是将于4月下旬开始的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/magdalena-bay-announce-2025-north-american-tour-dates-3821394">北美巡回演唱会</a>，并将在16场演出后于5月中旬结束，之后他们将踏上一轮<a href="https://imaginaldisk.world/tour" target="_blank" rel="noopener">欧洲节日的日期</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3821395" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3821395" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3821395" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/magdalena-bay@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/magdalena-bay@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/magdalena-bay@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/magdalena-bay@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/magdalena-bay@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/magdalena-bay@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/magdalena-bay@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3821395" class="wp-caption-text">玛格达莱纳湾（Magdalena bay</figcaption></figure><p>奥蒂斯·罗宾逊（Otis Robinson）在对“想象磁盘”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/magdalena-bay-imaginal-disk-review-3784463">五星级评论</a>中